snippet.title: The Odyssey | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
The Odyssey - In Theaters 07.17.26

Christopher Nolan‚Äôs next film, The Odyssey, is a mythic action epic shot across the world using brand new IMAX¬Æ film technology. The film brings Homer‚Äôs foundational saga to IMAX¬Æ film screens for the first time and opens in theaters everywhere on July 17, 2026. 

The Odyssey stars Matt Damon, Tom Holland, Anne Hathaway, Robert Pattinson and Lupita Nyong‚Äôo, with Zendaya and Charlize Theron.

The Odyssey is produced by Emma Thomas and Christopher Nolan for their company, Syncopy. The executive producer is Thomas Hayslip.

snippet.title: Dastan-E-Ma Gujri | Sandhu Surjit | Balraj | G Guri | GGM Entertainment | Devotional 2025
snippet.description:
‚ÄúDastan-E-Mata Gujri‚Äù is not just a song ‚Äî it is a sacred narration of Sikh history.
From the birth of Mata Gujri Ji to the journey of her life filled with faith, patience, and sacrifice,
this song beautifully portrays every chapter, leading up to the eternal martyrdom of the Chhote Sahibzade.
It is a heartfelt tribute to the unshakable courage of Mata Gujri Ji,
her spiritual strength, and her unwavering devotion to righteousness.
Each verse carries the pain, pride, and glory of a mother whose sacrifice shaped history.
This soulful composition is meant to touch every heart
that respects the legacy of Sikh martyrs and the timeless values they stood for.



Singer: Sandhu Surjit & Balraj
Music by: G Guri
Lyrics: Sandhu Surjit
Visual Vdo: Harsh Chopra 
MixMaster: Beat King 
Producer: G Guri & Amritpal Singh
Label: GGM Entertainment
